text.tspan: 10k resistors on top of the UP & DOWN pots: These can be tweaked to suit your vactrols
and your needs. The 10k pots convert the UP & DOWN pots into log pots.
10k gives a pretty linear line then a steep curve, 33k-47k give a more conservative arc.
